data.description: This stunning one-story home features 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, situated in a desirable neighborhood. As you enter, you'll be greeted by a long entryway with high ceilings and beautiful light brown laminate wood flooring that flows throughout the entire home. The open floor plan includes a formal dining area, a media room that can also be used as an office, and a spacious living room that seamlessly connects to the kitchen. The kitchen boasts white granite countertops, a white tile backsplash, and white cabinets, creating a clean and modern aesthetic. The master bedroom is generously sized and offers a tranquil retreat. Additional features of this home include epoxy floors in the garage, recessed lighting, a water softener, and a reverse osmosis system in the kitchen. Outside, you'll find a nice-sized backyard with a covered patio, perfect for outdoor entertaining or simply enjoying the peaceful surroundings. Don't miss the opportunity to make this fantastic property your new home.
